The method `public static Object getObjectFromPath(String path, Object source)` is supposed to be generic. However it contains a specific block with a strong dependence on `CollectionReferenceDescriptionProperty`. Removing this block might have an impact on classes trying to access properties on `CollectionReferenceDescriptionProperty`.

Code to remove:
```java
if (source instanceof CollectionReferenceDescriptionProperty
                    && ((CollectionReferenceDescriptionProperty) source).properties != null
                    && ((CollectionReferenceDescriptionProperty) source).properties.containsKey(pathLevels[0])) {
                return getObjectFromPath(newPath.toString(), ((CollectionReferenceDescriptionProperty) source).properties.get(pathLevels[0]));
            }
```

